Yeon-Seung Choi, the first human ever to become a celestial! He goes off to train in the Abyss to stop other celestials from swallowing Earth whole. Will he be able to protect Earth...?
(Source: Copin Comics)

Lee Hojae had given up his life as a pro gamer, until one day he received a mysterious message: Congratulations! Youve been invited to the Tutorial World. Intrigued, he enters the game and confidently chooses hell difficulty, but soon learns that he is trapped there. With a mere 0.01% survival rate, Hojae must somehow overcome the games agonizing challenges to figure out the real reason he was invited. This tutorial may be tough, but its secrets are whats truly hellacious. (Source: Tapas)
